1
00:00:01,070 --> 00:00:03,540
(Episode 71)

2
00:00:14,620 --> 00:00:17,020
Mom, what are you doing here?
Weren't you golfing with the Chairman?

3
00:00:17,120 --> 00:00:18,390
Do you really think
golf matters right now?

4
00:00:19,220 --> 00:00:20,830
We should've been one step ahead of her.

5
00:00:21,290 --> 00:00:23,290
Where is it? Where?
Which room is the twin in?

6
00:00:23,460 --> 00:00:24,830
- The elevator's here.
- Okay!

7
00:00:57,960 --> 00:00:59,030
It's here.

8
00:01:29,090 --> 00:01:30,130
What's wrong?

9
00:01:30,760 --> 00:01:32,100
I have a bad feeling about this.

10
00:01:33,930 --> 00:01:34,970
Let's go.

11
00:01:34,970 --> 00:01:37,500
I'll see the doctor first.

12
00:01:38,500 --> 00:01:39,500
Okay.

13
00:01:52,880 --> 00:01:54,090
Oh Tae Pyung.

14
00:01:54,090 --> 00:01:55,850
What are you doing here, CEO Chae?

15
00:01:57,690 --> 00:02:01,090
I heard Oh Jang Mi woke up,
so I thought I'd stop by.

16
00:02:01,960 --> 00:02:03,330
That's really odd.

17
00:02:04,630 --> 00:02:07,070
Why have you always been
so interested in Jang Mi?

18
00:02:07,570 --> 00:02:08,800
What's the reason?

19
00:02:08,800 --> 00:02:09,970
Reason?

20
00:02:10,600 --> 00:02:13,470
I was the one who was going to pay
for her to study abroad.

21
00:02:14,040 --> 00:02:16,640
It's natural for me to worry about her,
isn't it?

22
00:02:16,840 --> 00:02:18,210
Is that the only reason?

23
00:02:19,280 --> 00:02:20,280
Of course.

24
00:02:20,280 --> 00:02:23,580
A big-shot CEO like you is so busy,
but you still come...

25
00:02:24,380 --> 00:02:26,050
all the way to Jang Mi's room?

26
00:02:27,990 --> 00:02:29,390
Something about this doesn't add up.

27
00:02:34,060 --> 00:02:35,460
Tell me the truth.

28
00:02:36,030 --> 00:02:37,030
What is it?

29
00:02:38,100 --> 00:02:39,830
Did you come here to kill Jang Mi too?

30
00:02:40,130 --> 00:02:42,270
What? Watch your mouth!

31
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:44,070
You watch yours!

32
00:02:44,540 --> 00:02:48,510
It makes my blood boil to think
how you fooled me all this time.

33
00:02:48,770 --> 00:02:51,340
Baek Ho told me everything about you.

34
00:02:51,410 --> 00:02:53,310
What? Let go of me!

35
00:02:53,710 --> 00:02:57,020
Oh Jang Mi, I know you're awake!
Stop the act and get up!

36
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:58,750
Shut up, you monster!

37
00:02:58,820 --> 00:03:00,420
Why are you here?

38
00:03:00,420 --> 00:03:01,550
Let me go.

39
00:03:01,790 --> 00:03:04,560
Do you have any idea who I am?
How dare you treat me like this?

40
00:03:06,690 --> 00:03:08,060
Come to think of it,

41
00:03:08,060 --> 00:03:10,330
you sent the photo
of Kang Nam Bong, didn't you?

42
00:03:11,100 --> 00:03:14,700
Why did you send Kang Nam Bong's photo?

43
00:03:14,830 --> 00:03:15,970
Why?

44
00:03:17,000 --> 00:03:18,670
Do I need a reason to get my revenge?

45
00:03:19,940 --> 00:03:22,310
I can't even do that much to the man
who caused my father's death?

46
00:03:22,970 --> 00:03:24,280
What kind of son would I be if I didn't?

47
00:03:25,280 --> 00:03:26,840
- Revenge?
- That's right!

48
00:03:28,050 --> 00:03:31,080
And I'm going to make you pay for
everything you've done. You just wait.

49
00:03:32,680 --> 00:03:33,720
The nerve.

50
00:03:34,690 --> 00:03:36,920
You dare question me
after your affair with a married man?

51
00:03:36,920 --> 00:03:38,520
Have you no shame?

52
00:03:39,190 --> 00:03:42,730
Want me to expose you for the two-faced,
disgusting person you are?

53
00:03:43,060 --> 00:03:46,300
Should I go tell Lawyer Han Young Ja
what you two have been up to?

54
00:03:46,630 --> 00:03:47,670
Well?

55
00:03:49,100 --> 00:03:50,200
Why you...

56
00:03:53,170 --> 00:03:54,470
Stop it. Just stop.

57
00:03:58,880 --> 00:04:02,080
- I guess I struck a nerve.
- Shut up! Who do you think you are?

58
00:04:03,380 --> 00:04:04,380
Ma'am.

59
00:04:04,850 --> 00:04:06,620
Oh Jang Mi was discharged
from the hospital just now.

60
00:04:06,880 --> 00:04:07,950
What?

61
00:04:08,320 --> 00:04:09,590
Then who's this?

62
00:04:13,560 --> 00:04:15,590
- Oh Tae Pyung!
- You just wait.

63
00:04:16,030 --> 00:04:17,030
The two of you...

64
00:04:17,960 --> 00:04:20,030
will definitely pay for what you've done.

65
00:04:31,280 --> 00:04:33,140
Hey, Baek Ho.
You made it there safely, right?

66
00:04:33,650 --> 00:04:35,450
Where did Oh Jang Mi go?

67
00:04:35,510 --> 00:04:37,220
Probably to the side dish shop.

68
00:04:37,280 --> 00:04:39,620
She can't have gone far.
We have to find her.

69
00:04:39,680 --> 00:04:40,920
Yes, I'm on my way.

70
00:04:45,590 --> 00:04:48,960
Where did she go? Where?

71
00:04:49,460 --> 00:04:50,960
- It's over here. Mom, hurry.
- Okay.

72
00:04:51,300 --> 00:04:52,360
Oh my goodness!

73
00:04:56,070 --> 00:04:57,070
Yeom San Wol.

74
00:04:57,640 --> 00:04:58,770
What are you doing here?

75
00:04:59,970 --> 00:05:02,840
I could ask you the same thing,
dear daughter-in-law.

76
00:05:02,910 --> 00:05:04,240
I asked you first.

77
00:05:05,280 --> 00:05:09,010
I'm here to see someone I know.
Now, why are you here?

78
00:05:10,150 --> 00:05:12,150
I came to see the twins you gave birth to.
What about it?

79
00:05:12,220 --> 00:05:14,690
What? Who gave birth to twins?

80
00:05:14,750 --> 00:05:15,950
Does the Chairman know about this?

81
00:05:16,550 --> 00:05:19,160
That there's a twin
who's the spitting image of Ma Seo Rin.

82
00:05:19,860 --> 00:05:23,430
So the Chairman has
two granddaughters, then.

83
00:05:23,490 --> 00:05:24,600
Will you shut up?

84
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:27,100
What are you on about?

85
00:05:27,170 --> 00:05:30,370
Oh my. Look how defensive she gets
when we mention "twins."

86
00:05:30,570 --> 00:05:32,800
Hong Ju, the way she's reacting...

87
00:05:32,940 --> 00:05:34,970
proves that they must be twins.

88
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:38,780
I know her better than anyone.
She always reacts this way to the truth.

89
00:05:38,840 --> 00:05:41,350
- Oh, dear.
- Will you shut up?

90
00:05:41,810 --> 00:05:43,180
How dare you say that?

91
00:05:43,350 --> 00:05:45,580
- Did you see it with your eyes?
- Gosh, seriously.

92
00:05:45,580 --> 00:05:48,850
- Have you seen the twins yourself?
- Gosh, honestly...

93
00:05:50,520 --> 00:05:52,720
Hong Ju saw them!

94
00:05:52,860 --> 00:05:54,890
- Goodness.
- Hong Ju?

95
00:05:55,830 --> 00:05:59,030
How dare you run your mouth
based on what your daughter told you?

96
00:06:00,830 --> 00:06:02,670
If you ever...

97
00:06:03,070 --> 00:06:05,000
spout any more nonsense about twins,

98
00:06:05,000 --> 00:06:06,940
I'll tear that mouth right off your face.

99
00:06:10,940 --> 00:06:12,880
Oh dear, my mouth.

100
00:06:12,880 --> 00:06:13,880
Darn it!

101
00:06:15,550 --> 00:06:19,550
I can't believe a CEO
can be so foul-mouthed.

102
00:06:19,620 --> 00:06:20,620
Tell me about it.

103
00:06:20,950 --> 00:06:22,690
No wonder that video
of her power trip went viral.

104
00:06:22,820 --> 00:06:25,360
So, where is this twin then?

105
00:06:25,890 --> 00:06:27,660
Is this even the right room?

106
00:06:45,280 --> 00:06:46,880
Did you get a chance
to talk to the doctor?

107
00:06:47,250 --> 00:06:48,250
Yes.

108
00:06:48,580 --> 00:06:50,450
It's not about medical treatment now,

109
00:06:50,720 --> 00:06:54,290
but rather preventing bedsores
and other illnesses like pneumonia.

110
00:06:54,290 --> 00:06:55,420
That's the best they can do.

111
00:06:55,850 --> 00:06:57,820
The chances of her regaining consciousness
are pretty low, too.

112
00:06:58,390 --> 00:07:02,360
Still, let's have faith in Seo Rin.
I'm sure she'll wake up.

113
00:07:02,830 --> 00:07:05,500
Now that Chae Hwa Young thinks
I've woken up,

114
00:07:05,830 --> 00:07:07,670
she'll be even more desperate to find me.

115
00:07:07,870 --> 00:07:09,300
You have to be careful, Jang Mi.

116
00:07:09,670 --> 00:07:13,000
CEO Chae will be frantic,
afraid the truth about the twins gets out.

117
00:07:17,410 --> 00:07:20,850
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

118
00:07:25,580 --> 00:07:26,980
Keep a close watch on Oh Tae Pyung.

119
00:07:28,290 --> 00:07:31,460
It was Oh Jang Mi and Oh Tae Pyung
behind everything all along.

120
00:07:31,660 --> 00:07:35,390
I've had my men tailing Oh Tae Pyung,
so we should find Oh Jang Mi soon.

121
00:07:35,590 --> 00:07:39,760
It seems they know I killed their father.

122
00:07:40,770 --> 00:07:43,670
If that's true,
they'll stop at nothing to come after me.

123
00:07:43,800 --> 00:07:45,040
I will make sure we are fully prepared.

124
00:07:54,810 --> 00:07:57,080
Tae Pyung, look. It's Ok Hee, a bunny.

125
00:07:57,080 --> 00:07:58,620
Suk Hee drew it.

126
00:07:59,420 --> 00:08:01,390
Grandma, what kind of drawing is that?

127
00:08:01,590 --> 00:08:03,650
It's just a bunch of circles.

128
00:08:26,940 --> 00:08:31,320
I wonder if my Jun Ho
tried calling me again.

129
00:08:36,350 --> 00:08:38,090
Let's meet at Han River Park at seven.

130
00:08:38,790 --> 00:08:40,290
If you don't show up today,

131
00:08:40,660 --> 00:08:41,690
I will never...

132
00:08:42,330 --> 00:08:43,430
ever...

133
00:08:43,560 --> 00:08:45,260
contact you or look for you again.

134
00:08:46,460 --> 00:08:47,700
My Jun Ho...

135
00:08:48,570 --> 00:08:50,770
Jun Ho is desperate to see me.

136
00:08:54,340 --> 00:08:55,770
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

137
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:56,940
Kang Hyuk, what should I do?

138
00:08:57,140 --> 00:08:58,640
Jun Ho called me.

139
00:08:59,080 --> 00:09:00,650
He wants to meet me somewhere.

140
00:09:01,210 --> 00:09:02,380
Are you going to meet him?

141
00:09:02,810 --> 00:09:05,320
He's only ever seen me at my worst.

142
00:09:05,750 --> 00:09:08,150
Besides, I haven't even managed
to get Seo Rin married yet.

143
00:09:08,920 --> 00:09:13,490
It's better if I reveal I'm his mother
much later.

144
00:09:14,760 --> 00:09:16,990
Then General Manager Kang
will go there by himself.

145
00:09:17,900 --> 00:09:19,630
He'll probably be extremely disappointed.

146
00:09:20,460 --> 00:09:23,200
He'll think his mother has abandoned him
for a second time.

147
00:09:24,140 --> 00:09:25,440
My poor boy.

148
00:09:26,240 --> 00:09:28,170
I don't know what to do.

149
00:09:28,540 --> 00:09:32,080
If you've decided not to see him,
then you need to stick to your decision.

150
00:09:32,740 --> 00:09:33,740
One more thing.

151
00:09:34,450 --> 00:09:35,950
I checked out that side dish shop,

152
00:09:36,280 --> 00:09:38,480
and it doesn't look like
they moved Oh Jang Mi there.

153
00:09:39,920 --> 00:09:40,920
Really?

154
00:09:40,990 --> 00:09:43,590
(General Manager Kang Jun Ho)

155
00:09:50,390 --> 00:09:52,860
She read my text but hasn't replied?

156
00:09:53,660 --> 00:09:55,670
So is she coming or not?

157
00:09:57,100 --> 00:09:58,800
So this is how you're going to be?

158
00:09:59,940 --> 00:10:00,940
No.

159
00:10:01,340 --> 00:10:03,770
She must have seen my text
and is probably thinking it over now.

160
00:10:11,280 --> 00:10:12,820
Even if it's just from a distance,

161
00:10:13,480 --> 00:10:16,220
I have to see Jun Ho
waiting to meet his mother.

162
00:10:18,590 --> 00:10:19,960
Imagine how long he'll wait.

163
00:10:20,790 --> 00:10:23,330
How much he must have longed
to finally meet his mother.

164
00:10:23,830 --> 00:10:24,830
What?

165
00:10:25,500 --> 00:10:27,530
Then shall I take you to Han River Park
at 7 p.m.?

166
00:10:27,770 --> 00:10:29,170
No, I'll go alone.

167
00:10:29,700 --> 00:10:31,540
I'm not planning on meeting him
face-to-face.

168
00:10:32,270 --> 00:10:37,140
I just need to see from a distance
if my Jun Ho is heartbroken or not.

169
00:10:37,210 --> 00:10:39,180
Only then will I be able
to put my mind at ease.

170
00:10:41,050 --> 00:10:42,210
I must pray,

171
00:10:43,110 --> 00:10:46,420
even from a distance, that my son
will be strong and pull through.

172
00:10:47,990 --> 00:10:50,960
(General Manager Kang Jun Ho)

173
00:10:57,660 --> 00:11:00,600
No. The woman who gave birth to me...

174
00:11:01,270 --> 00:11:02,500
can't be CEO Chae.

175
00:11:03,700 --> 00:11:06,900
I have her vile blood in me?

176
00:11:11,080 --> 00:11:12,780
This is impossible.

177
00:11:13,710 --> 00:11:14,910
It can't be true.

178
00:11:16,980 --> 00:11:19,050
CEO Chae Hwa Young is my mother?

179
00:11:22,190 --> 00:11:24,060
Sir, you know about the meeting today...

180
00:11:24,460 --> 00:11:27,120
You know, right?
Can you give me the files?

181
00:11:30,930 --> 00:11:31,930
Director Ma.

182
00:11:32,260 --> 00:11:34,900
Yes? Is something wrong?

183
00:11:35,630 --> 00:11:36,630
This is...

184
00:11:39,100 --> 00:11:40,100
Never mind.

185
00:11:41,410 --> 00:11:42,740
Let's just cancel today's meeting.

186
00:11:43,070 --> 00:11:45,880
Wait, is something wrong?

187
00:11:47,410 --> 00:11:48,610
I said it was nothing.

188
00:11:49,180 --> 00:11:51,380
Did I do something wrong?

189
00:11:54,450 --> 00:11:55,490
I'm sorry.

190
00:11:57,250 --> 00:11:58,990
Could you please leave, Director Ma?

191
00:11:59,220 --> 00:12:00,860
Yes, of course.

192
00:12:02,390 --> 00:12:04,400
(General Manager Kang Jun Ho)

193
00:12:10,330 --> 00:12:13,240
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

194
00:12:26,420 --> 00:12:27,950
I've changed my mind.

195
00:12:28,590 --> 00:12:31,420
It would be best if we lived our lives
as strangers forever.

196
00:12:31,990 --> 00:12:36,060
I heard you told the center's director
that you wouldn't meet me.

197
00:12:36,690 --> 00:12:40,000
Fine. Then I won't be meeting you, either.

198
00:12:40,660 --> 00:12:43,200
I hope that your life,
never being able to meet me,

199
00:12:43,530 --> 00:12:45,240
is a living hell forever.

200
00:12:46,200 --> 00:12:47,940
Don't you ever be happy.

201
00:12:49,840 --> 00:12:50,840
I'm so sorry.

202
00:12:51,440 --> 00:12:52,610
I'm so sorry, Jun Ho.

203
00:12:54,010 --> 00:12:55,010
My son...

204
00:12:55,750 --> 00:12:57,680
He's hurt, and he resents me.

205
00:12:58,780 --> 00:12:59,820
What do I do?

206
00:13:01,250 --> 00:13:04,050
I've hurt my Jun Ho twice now.

207
00:13:05,190 --> 00:13:06,460
I'm so sorry, Jun Ho.

208
00:13:07,160 --> 00:13:08,160
I'm so sorry.

209
00:13:09,790 --> 00:13:12,730
How could I ever be happy without you?

210
00:13:14,170 --> 00:13:15,170
I'm so sorry.

211
00:13:15,970 --> 00:13:17,230
I'm so sorry, my son.

212
00:13:33,720 --> 00:13:34,890
It seemed like...

213
00:13:34,890 --> 00:13:37,390
CEO Chae didn't know where Oh Jang Mi
had been transferred, either.

214
00:13:37,620 --> 00:13:40,020
If Oh Jang Mi and Ma Seo Rin are twins,

215
00:13:40,020 --> 00:13:43,690
the Chairman must see them both together
for it to be the knockout punch.

216
00:13:43,760 --> 00:13:46,700
Mom, I saw them! They look like twins!

217
00:13:46,760 --> 00:13:49,230
Gosh, but I haven't seen them, have I?

218
00:13:49,500 --> 00:13:52,700
It's already suspicious that
CEO Chae visited Oh Jang Mi's room.

219
00:13:53,470 --> 00:13:54,470
You have a point.

220
00:13:55,010 --> 00:13:56,840
But if they are twins,

221
00:13:57,580 --> 00:14:00,910
why would she give birth to them
but only raise Seo Rin...

222
00:14:01,210 --> 00:14:03,410
and leave Oh Jang Mi to be raised
by that simpleton?

223
00:14:03,550 --> 00:14:05,150
It could be the other way around,
you know.

224
00:14:05,480 --> 00:14:07,080
What? The other way around?

225
00:14:07,220 --> 00:14:09,650
What if Oh Jang Mi's mom had the twins,

226
00:14:09,790 --> 00:14:12,790
and CEO Chae is the one
who stole Ma Seo Rin?

227
00:14:14,120 --> 00:14:16,590
- Oh my goodness.
- Hold on a second, Mom.

228
00:14:16,730 --> 00:14:17,730
Alright.

229
00:14:20,630 --> 00:14:23,070
Oh my, if this is true,

230
00:14:23,770 --> 00:14:27,140
the Chairman has been conned
by CEO Chae all this time.

231
00:14:28,110 --> 00:14:29,110
My goodness.

232
00:14:29,570 --> 00:14:33,340
I wonder if Tae Pyung knows
his sister is a twin.

233
00:14:35,050 --> 00:14:38,020
Gosh, this is a bombshell.

234
00:14:38,150 --> 00:14:39,480
If we expose this,

235
00:14:39,620 --> 00:14:42,650
we could make Chae Hwa Young our maid...

236
00:14:43,090 --> 00:14:46,360
and get revenge for all the humiliation
she's put us through.

237
00:14:47,320 --> 00:14:48,730
What a stroke of luck!

238
00:14:55,470 --> 00:14:56,630
Let's get a DNA test done...

239
00:14:56,630 --> 00:14:58,240
between CEO Chae
and Ma Seo Rin right away.

240
00:14:58,340 --> 00:14:59,840
Yes, that's it!

241
00:15:02,470 --> 00:15:05,840
Why are you suddenly making dumplings?
You're so busy with work.

242
00:15:06,380 --> 00:15:10,480
The housekeeper made the filling,
so all we have to do is wrap them.

243
00:15:11,280 --> 00:15:13,220
Besides, you know
how much your dad loves dumplings.

244
00:15:15,750 --> 00:15:17,450
Mom, what if...

245
00:15:18,460 --> 00:15:19,690
This is purely hypothetical, but...

246
00:15:19,820 --> 00:15:20,920
What are you getting at?

247
00:15:21,260 --> 00:15:23,460
You trust Dad so much,

248
00:15:24,130 --> 00:15:27,770
but what would you do
if he ever betrayed you?

249
00:15:27,900 --> 00:15:29,630
How can you ask that?
You know your father.

250
00:15:31,700 --> 00:15:36,440
Your father would never betray me.
Not in a million years.

251
00:15:38,040 --> 00:15:41,410
All he cares about
when he's not working is you, boys.

252
00:15:41,410 --> 00:15:42,880
He's a total family man.

253
00:15:44,280 --> 00:15:46,920
I'm so happy I met your father.

254
00:15:47,420 --> 00:15:49,120
Men like him are one in a million.

255
00:15:49,590 --> 00:15:51,120
Mom, give it a rest.

256
00:15:51,520 --> 00:15:53,160
What are you going to do
if that comes back to bite you?

257
00:15:55,130 --> 00:15:56,430
I'm home.

258
00:15:57,160 --> 00:16:00,700
Hey, you're making dumplings!

259
00:16:00,800 --> 00:16:04,870
You love dumplings.
We're having dumpling hot pot for dinner.

260
00:16:04,940 --> 00:16:05,940
Sounds delicious, right?

261
00:16:06,000 --> 00:16:07,640
Gosh, that sounds amazing.

262
00:16:07,640 --> 00:16:09,370
I was just starting to get hungry, too.

263
00:16:09,440 --> 00:16:11,040
Dad, can I talk to you for a second?

264
00:16:15,080 --> 00:16:16,080
What's with him?

265
00:16:17,080 --> 00:16:18,080
Goodness.

266
00:16:24,220 --> 00:16:26,720
What are you doing?
Do you want your mom to find out?

267
00:16:26,790 --> 00:16:28,360
Are you that scared of Mom finding out?

268
00:16:28,860 --> 00:16:30,260
Then why are you cheating on her?

269
00:16:31,960 --> 00:16:33,860
- Keep your voice down.
- I told you...

270
00:16:34,230 --> 00:16:35,800
to stop seeing CEO Chae.

271
00:16:36,470 --> 00:16:39,500
- This is none of your business.
- I'm your son...

272
00:16:39,840 --> 00:16:41,740
and the son of the mother I love.

273
00:16:42,010 --> 00:16:44,310
I can't stand to see Mom cry.

274
00:16:44,980 --> 00:16:48,550
Then just keep it a secret.
Ignorance is bliss.

275
00:16:48,610 --> 00:16:49,750
Dad, what's gotten into you?

276
00:16:50,510 --> 00:16:53,980
I used to respect you so much.
You were my role model.

277
00:16:54,320 --> 00:16:55,820
How can you say something like that?

278
00:16:55,820 --> 00:16:58,460
That's enough. Just drop it.

279
00:16:58,560 --> 00:17:01,590
So your logic is that it's not a sin
as long as you don't get caught.

280
00:17:01,890 --> 00:17:03,530
There's a limit to making
a fool out of Mom.

281
00:17:04,330 --> 00:17:07,260
Dad, if you keep this up,
I may never see you again.

282
00:17:07,730 --> 00:17:09,070
That's a scary threat.

283
00:17:09,600 --> 00:17:12,240
Don't talk to your father like that
just because you're grown up, okay?

284
00:17:12,240 --> 00:17:13,700
As a man,
you can't understand your father...

285
00:17:13,700 --> 00:17:14,710
Dad.

286
00:17:15,040 --> 00:17:17,710
Fine, I get it. I'll end it, okay?

287
00:17:18,810 --> 00:17:19,880
End what?

288
00:17:20,610 --> 00:17:22,180
Nothing.

289
00:17:22,510 --> 00:17:25,150
He just asked me to organize
my books on his bookshelf.

290
00:17:25,250 --> 00:17:27,180
The dumplings are ready. Come on out.

291
00:17:27,580 --> 00:17:30,390
What's all the intense whispering about?

292
00:17:30,590 --> 00:17:31,860
You're making me jealous.

293
00:17:32,290 --> 00:17:34,460
I wish Jun Ho were here to eat with us.

294
00:17:34,660 --> 00:17:36,530
Right. The kimchi dumplings are all mine.

295
00:17:36,790 --> 00:17:38,160
Honestly.

296
00:17:55,680 --> 00:17:58,280
You're testing my patience,
you arrogant punk!

297
00:17:58,350 --> 00:17:59,920
Let go of me.

298
00:18:07,160 --> 00:18:08,160
Jun Ho!

299
00:18:08,160 --> 00:18:09,490
Oh, my gosh, you're bleeding.

300
00:18:09,960 --> 00:18:11,530
Are you out of your mind?

301
00:18:12,330 --> 00:18:13,330
Mom!

302
00:18:40,620 --> 00:18:44,290
Why was I born to a woman like you?

303
00:18:44,800 --> 00:18:46,160
I would've been fine...

304
00:18:46,530 --> 00:18:49,800
if I hadn't been born to a heartless,
cold-blooded, vicious woman like you.

305
00:18:50,270 --> 00:18:54,340
Of all people,
why did you have to give birth to me?

306
00:19:10,150 --> 00:19:11,720
I'm so sorry, Jun Ho.

307
00:19:12,660 --> 00:19:13,790
I'm so sorry, my baby.

308
00:19:14,590 --> 00:19:15,890
Please forgive me.

309
00:19:17,290 --> 00:19:20,160
My poor son, you must be so hurt.

310
00:19:22,930 --> 00:19:23,930
Mom.

311
00:19:25,740 --> 00:19:26,870
Is something wrong?

312
00:19:27,740 --> 00:19:28,810
Why are you crying?

313
00:19:29,240 --> 00:19:32,240
It's nothing.
It's just the state I'm in these days.

314
00:19:33,440 --> 00:19:35,180
Want me to make you some honey tea?

315
00:19:35,950 --> 00:19:37,110
Would you, please?

316
00:19:47,160 --> 00:19:48,890
Get it together, Chae Hwa Young.

317
00:19:55,570 --> 00:19:58,640
- What is it?
- I saw Kang Baek Ho at the house.

318
00:19:59,270 --> 00:20:01,970
- But I don't think he met Oh Jang Mi.
- Are you sure?

319
00:20:02,740 --> 00:20:05,280
I'm sure Kang Baek Ho is helping her.

320
00:20:06,210 --> 00:20:09,350
- So is she hiding somewhere else?
- That's possible.

321
00:20:10,180 --> 00:20:12,750
Either way, I'll find out
where Oh Jang Mi is soon.

322
00:20:13,050 --> 00:20:14,890
Right. Find her immediately.

323
00:20:15,420 --> 00:20:17,190
They could strike at any moment.

324
00:20:30,700 --> 00:20:32,370
Something's suspicious
about Chae Hwa Young.

325
00:20:32,940 --> 00:20:34,840
I have to see what she was looking at.

326
00:20:51,720 --> 00:20:53,360
Who is this child?

327
00:20:54,190 --> 00:20:56,690
Why was Chae Hwa Young
crying over this photo?

328
00:20:59,360 --> 00:21:01,730
This is my mom's hairpin.

329
00:21:12,410 --> 00:21:14,950
Seo Rin. What are you doing in here?

330
00:21:16,110 --> 00:21:19,780
I just remembered that
you and honey don't go well together.

331
00:21:19,980 --> 00:21:22,420
So I came back to ask
what you'd like instead.

332
00:21:22,490 --> 00:21:24,250
Where did you run off to, Mom?

333
00:21:24,960 --> 00:21:27,060
- Really?
- I'll get you a different tea.

334
00:21:43,140 --> 00:21:44,170
What was that?

335
00:21:44,440 --> 00:21:46,410
Why was that hairpin
on the baby's clothes?

336
00:21:47,340 --> 00:21:49,150
What happened to my mom's hairpin?

337
00:21:51,180 --> 00:21:52,780
You moved Jang Mi to another hospital?

338
00:21:53,580 --> 00:21:54,580
Why?

339
00:21:54,850 --> 00:21:56,220
Something came up.

340
00:21:56,750 --> 00:21:58,920
So just don't go
to that hospital room, okay?

341
00:21:59,190 --> 00:22:00,820
Did you move her
because of the hospital bills?

342
00:22:01,120 --> 00:22:02,460
So where did you move her?

343
00:22:02,460 --> 00:22:04,190
You can't know this secret.

344
00:22:04,460 --> 00:22:05,600
You'll be in danger too.

345
00:22:05,600 --> 00:22:08,370
What? What are you talking about?

346
00:22:08,600 --> 00:22:09,770
Spit it out, already!

347
00:22:11,800 --> 00:22:14,240
Then you must swear to keep it a secret.

348
00:22:14,970 --> 00:22:16,570
Or else our Jang Mi will be in danger.

349
00:22:17,610 --> 00:22:18,610
The thing is,

350
00:22:19,580 --> 00:22:21,710
the person in a coma
at the hospital right now...

351
00:22:22,350 --> 00:22:23,850
isn't Jang Mi. It's Ma Seo Rin.

352
00:22:24,850 --> 00:22:26,180
Jang Mi and Ma Seo Rin...

353
00:22:27,380 --> 00:22:28,420
are twins.

354
00:22:28,720 --> 00:22:29,750
What?

355
00:22:30,150 --> 00:22:31,420
Twins?

356
00:22:33,220 --> 00:22:36,130
I have to go to Dream Hotel tomorrow,

357
00:22:36,460 --> 00:22:38,360
so get my suit ready.

358
00:22:38,560 --> 00:22:40,530
You've been going
to Dream Hotel a lot lately.

359
00:22:40,900 --> 00:22:45,140
I suppose you're busy
cleaning up the mess CEO Chae made.

360
00:22:45,200 --> 00:22:46,200
Grandfather.

361
00:22:47,500 --> 00:22:49,140
Don't push yourself too hard.

362
00:22:50,010 --> 00:22:52,610
Mom said she wanted a cup of tea,
so I was just going to make some.

363
00:22:52,680 --> 00:22:54,110
Would you like a cup too, Grandfather?

364
00:22:54,110 --> 00:22:55,250
No, that's all right, Seo Rin.

365
00:22:56,680 --> 00:22:59,220
My sweet girl.
It looks like you're finally growing up.

366
00:22:59,650 --> 00:23:01,080
Even thinking of comforting your mom.

367
00:23:06,860 --> 00:23:08,960
So Grandfather is coming
to Dream Hotel tomorrow?

368
00:23:09,860 --> 00:23:12,300
All right. Just you wait, Chae Hwa Young.

369
00:23:12,830 --> 00:23:17,330
I'll expose you for ruining my life,
Seo Rin's, and my mother's.

370
00:23:22,710 --> 00:23:25,440
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

371
00:23:28,310 --> 00:23:30,080
I can't believe this is the woman
who gave birth to me.

372
00:23:30,980 --> 00:23:32,220
Of all people, it had to be her.

373
00:23:34,990 --> 00:23:36,590
Didn't you sleep well last night?

374
00:23:37,490 --> 00:23:39,020
You look a little worn out.

375
00:23:39,160 --> 00:23:40,190
Not at all.

376
00:23:40,490 --> 00:23:41,990
I got a workout in
for the first time in a while,

377
00:23:42,560 --> 00:23:44,460
and I slept like a log.

378
00:23:45,860 --> 00:23:47,560
If anything, you're the one
who looks unwell, ma'am.

379
00:23:48,300 --> 00:23:50,300
Your face is puffy,
as if you cried all night.

380
00:23:52,470 --> 00:23:53,840
I guess I'm just tired.

381
00:23:54,670 --> 00:23:55,670
I suppose.

382
00:23:56,040 --> 00:23:57,240
The fallout
from the power trip controversy...

383
00:23:57,240 --> 00:23:58,480
must have been huge.

384
00:23:59,040 --> 00:24:00,380
It's no wonder you're exhausted.

385
00:24:01,110 --> 00:24:03,110
General Manager Kang,
are you angry with me about something?

386
00:24:04,180 --> 00:24:05,650
There's an edge to your words.

387
00:24:05,880 --> 00:24:08,220
Why would I have any reason
to be angry with you, ma'am?

388
00:24:25,440 --> 00:24:28,000
Don't play the victim
with that shameless face of yours.

389
00:24:28,810 --> 00:24:30,040
It's disgusting.

390
00:24:33,440 --> 00:24:34,810
And you're my mother?

391
00:24:36,250 --> 00:24:37,250
Don't make me laugh.

392
00:24:38,580 --> 00:24:40,580
You're not the woman who gave birth to me.

393
00:24:42,050 --> 00:24:43,550
Not even if I died and came back to life.

394
00:24:44,050 --> 00:24:48,460
I will never be your son,
so don't even dream of it.

395
00:24:49,960 --> 00:24:52,460
- Jun Ho.
- You abandoned me as a newborn,

396
00:24:53,560 --> 00:24:54,870
and now you're calling me your son?

397
00:24:56,770 --> 00:25:00,000
Why did you come to the orphanage
just to act like you didn't know me?

398
00:25:01,200 --> 00:25:02,210
And what's this?

399
00:25:02,870 --> 00:25:04,440
Now you want to marry me off...

400
00:25:05,210 --> 00:25:06,610
to your daughter?

401
00:25:06,810 --> 00:25:08,650
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

402
00:25:11,950 --> 00:25:14,080
Why? Tell me why!

403
00:25:30,470 --> 00:25:32,970
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

404
00:25:38,240 --> 00:25:40,240
Mrs. Yang? Geum Soon?

405
00:25:46,120 --> 00:25:47,180
Where is she?

406
00:25:47,780 --> 00:25:49,550
Where could that woman have gone?

407
00:25:50,550 --> 00:25:51,790
Goodness.

408
00:25:52,120 --> 00:25:55,390
I should go while Chairman Ma is away
to see my Tae Pyung.

409
00:25:56,890 --> 00:25:59,800
If I don't see him for even a day,
I miss him like crazy.

410
00:26:01,060 --> 00:26:02,400
It's so upsetting.

411
00:26:04,940 --> 00:26:06,000
By the way, I wonder if Hong Ju...

412
00:26:06,840 --> 00:26:08,970
managed to get that DNA test submitted.

413
00:26:14,480 --> 00:26:15,980
You're keeping a close eye
on Oh Tae Pyung, right?

414
00:26:16,780 --> 00:26:19,280
- Yes.
- Put a tail on Yeom San Wol too.

415
00:26:19,850 --> 00:26:20,880
Understood.

416
00:26:43,410 --> 00:26:44,410
Who are you?

417
00:26:53,520 --> 00:26:54,520
Oh Jang Mi?

418
00:27:11,940 --> 00:27:14,000
- You're here, Chairman.
- Yes.

419
00:27:14,900 --> 00:27:17,770
So, Lawyer Kang,
how are you liking the company?

420
00:27:18,110 --> 00:27:20,540
It's been great.
Thank you for looking out for me, sir.

421
00:27:21,080 --> 00:27:23,550
- Are you here to see CEO Chae?
- Yes.

422
00:27:24,150 --> 00:27:25,320
I'll show you in.

423
00:27:25,450 --> 00:27:26,480
Thanks.

424
00:27:31,820 --> 00:27:34,590
You're Oh Jang Mi.

425
00:27:35,430 --> 00:27:38,060
That's right. It's me, Oh Jang Mi.

426
00:27:38,900 --> 00:27:41,730
The very same Oh Jang Mi
you tried so desperately to kill.

427
00:28:12,360 --> 00:28:13,830
(The First Man)

428
00:28:13,900 --> 00:28:15,000
Oh Jang Mi.

429
00:28:15,000 --> 00:28:17,300
You had me completely fooled
all this time.

430
00:28:17,670 --> 00:28:19,270
You shameless, evil witch.

431
00:28:19,340 --> 00:28:22,070
- Chairman Ma is on his way.
- The Chairman?

432
00:28:22,210 --> 00:28:24,670
While I was fighting for my life
with leukemia,

433
00:28:24,810 --> 00:28:26,740
you were living it up like this?

434
00:28:27,110 --> 00:28:28,510
I can never forgive you.

435
00:28:28,780 --> 00:28:30,110
The Chairman can't come in here.

436
00:28:30,180 --> 00:28:31,580
I'm going to see the Chairman right now.

437
00:28:31,650 --> 00:28:32,720
No, you can't!

438
00:28:32,850 --> 00:28:34,220
You're finished.

439
00:28:40,060 --> 00:28:42,060
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
